Class MatrixBaseNDArrayList<X extends BaseNDArrayList>

    FloatMatrixNDArrayList, IntMatrixNDArrayList, MatrixNDArrayList

    public abstract class MatrixBaseNDArrayList<X extends BaseNDArrayList>
extends java.util.AbstractList<X>
    An ArrayList like implementation of List using INDArray as the backing data structure. Creates an internal container of ndarray lists with a matrix shape.

      • array

        public INDArray array()
        Get a view of the underlying array relative to the size of the actual array. (Sometimes there are overflows in the internals but you want to use the internal INDArray for computing something directly, this gives you the relevant subset that reflects the content of the list)
        Returns:
        the view of the underlying ndarray relative to the collection's real size
